*Vesti* su se širile brzo. (The news spread quickly.)

Nikad pre nismo čuli takve *vesti*. (We had never heard such news before.)

Ona je donela loše *vesti*. (She brought bad news.)

Njegovo ime se spominje u *vestima*. (His name is mentioned in the news.)

Novinar je istraživao *vesti*. (The journalist was investigating the news.)

Mislio je da će *vesti* biti dobre. (He thought the news would be good.)